name: Sainsburys Sherborne
directions: Directly to the left upon entrance to the store
comment: Disabled bathroom is gender neutral. Sign on door says "not all disabilities are visible" and I have a non-visible disability, so definitely a safe space. Kept really clean and generally really good. Sink is nice and low and there are bars if you have mobility issues, as well as extra bars on the door to assist with closing/opening. You don't need to buy anything to use it but there is a fee for the store parking lot.
